	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;   Why use a horn when you can /disc puretone ? the level 60 discipline is as good or better than any  instrument bonus out there. So lets assume that you have used /disc for a moment.... now if you are in a raid guild  you should  have at least an 11/18 weapon or better. Attacking will yield far more damage then using horn. No small bonus is worth giving up meager bard DPS with weapon. IMHO this is only useful for sub level 60 bards and very rarely useful for them. <br><br>Muse Sournote<br>65 bard of Xev<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=430827" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=430827</a><br>edit fix broken link <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Mar 19 20:37:40 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
